wdi-BX.PEF.TOTL.CD.WD.def: Portfolio equity includes net inflows from equity securities other than those recorded as direct investment and including shares, stocks, depository receipts (American or global), and direct purchases of shares in local stock markets by foreign investors. Data are in current U.S. dollars.
wdi-BX.PEF.TOTL.CD.WD.name: Portfolio equity, net inflows
wdi-BX.PEF.TOTL.CD.WD.source: International Monetary Fund, Balance of Payments database, and World Bank, International Debt Statistics.
